data.description: Fantastic starter home that features completely fenced-in backyard w/ a canal. This home features 3 bedrooms 1 1/2 bath and a screened lanai. New paint on the interior in the home. This home is located off Lee Blvd on city water & sewer. Wonderful location surrounded single family homes w/ lots of shopping & dining options close by. New roof 2018 & Kitchen was remolded in 2018. New aluminum Hurricane Shutters. "Motivated Seller accepting all offers"
